VAMPIRIC TOUCH

Usage       : cast 'vampiric touch' <target>
Accumulative: -
Duration    : instantaneous
Save        : Versus spell

   When an anti-paladin casts this spell, it sucks a moderate amount of energy
from whomever it is cast upon.  This energy is added to the black knight's
hit points.  The amount of damage is dependant on level.

See Also: LIFE LEECH
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
